---
title: Hawaiian-Inspired Bacon Fried Rice with Pineapple, Bok Choy and Green Onion
description: Prepare your taste buds for this bacon fried rice with a Hawaiian-inspired pineapple twist! Green onions and bok choy round out this one-pan wonder!
